    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a pristine 997.1 Carrera S, an analog masterpiece for the discerning driver. This example features the 3.8L M97 flat-six, delivering 355 hp through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical synchronization is flawless, with the factory PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) providing exceptional lateral stability. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, including a proactive IMS bearing upgrade and a recent borescope inspection confirming zero scoring. The naturally aspirated induction note is crisp, and the gear engagement remains tight and communicative. Finished with staggered 19-inch 'Lobster Claw' alloys and a high-rigidity chassis that feels as taut as the day it left Zuffenhausen.",
